# RunNode business cloud base URL. Compiled into the renderer build via
# vite's `define` block, and read at runtime by the main process from
# `process.env.VITE_CLOUD_API_BASE_URL` (vite-plugin-electron forwards it
# in dev mode).
#
# When this variable is unset, the main process falls back to the
# canonical RunNode production URL (see DEFAULT_CLOUD_API_BASE_URL in
# src/main/utils/cloudApiBaseUrl.ts). Override here if you need to point
# at staging or a private deployment.
VITE_CLOUD_API_BASE_URL=https://www.runnode.cn